snippet.title: Super Mega Baseball 4 (Switch) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full nine-inning game of Super Mega Baseball 4 on Nintendo Switch. This is using the "favor performance" mode in the settings, which I definitely recommend on Switch. The default "favor resolution" setting makes it really hard to time swings and throws with the framerate. 

Compare against these other versions:

PC: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PApsHQ1KN8E
PS5: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qUbRlDtxrv8
